creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink: Unlimited friends! Wink is the best place to make new friends from all over the world. It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

So...what exactly do you do on the Wink app?

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through a bunch of new faces! Does that guy have the same quote in his bio as you do?! SWIPE RIGHT! Instant friends. She likes the soccer team that you hate the most?! SWIPE LEFT! No chance of a friendship there! On Wink, you can meet new friends in your country and around the world. You can add them on Snapchat, or start up a conversation right on Wink. You’ll see tons of new faces, read about them in their bios, and decide who you really want to be Wink friends or snap friends with! Start swiping to meet your new pals!

ADD
When you request to add someone or they request to add you, Wink makes it super easy to add the new friends you’re meeting to Wink and on Snapchat. With the click of a button, you become instantly connected! You go from a swipe on Wink, right to being friends!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new Wink friends is to start up the conversation right here on Wink! You have the option to add them on Snapchat as well, but why not chat a bit first? Get to know your new friends. Find out what you have in common! Who knows, someone you start messaging on Wink could become your lifelong best friend.

EARN
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on Wink! What are the gems used for, you ask? You can use gems to send add requests to your new friends, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing Wink with your existing snap friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. If you keep earning gems, unlimited friends is truly what there is on Wink.

Basically, what I’m trying to say is... you can never have too many friends. And tbh, it can be hard to make friends sometimes. All the awkwardness and asking for numbers and Snapchats and whatever. Wink exists to help you easily put yourself out there, and find more and more people to make your life even more fun! All you have to do is create your profile, tell everyone who you are, and start to discover your future besties.

But wait...there’s more! There are some other major bonuses to using Wink. Remember how I said you can not only chat with your new friends on the Wink app? Well you can also add them on Snapchat super easily! The more new friends you make and add to snap, the more views you get on your Snapchat story. You could go from 50 to 500 people watching! You’ll also have even more people to start snap streaks with (just make sure to keep those alive)!

Say yolo and just do it. Download the Wink app, put yourself out there, and see all of the cool people you can find by sitting there and mindlessly swiping while you watch TV even though you’re supposed to be doing homework. What do you have to lose? Go meet people to become friends with!!

PS - Wink is for friendships ONLY. Thank you.

Safety disclaimer: Wink is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with on both Wink and Snapchat Snapchat. Although this communication with new friends doesn’t always happen on our platform, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing their location, full name, and all other personal information with new friends. Additionally, Wink is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Account selling, or requesting adult content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. Please report anything you see that isn’t right!

Have feedback on Wink? Lmk what you like, don’t like, want to add, etc by emailing support@getwinkapp.com.

;) Wink
descriptionShort: Swipe to meet new friends! Increase your Snapchat story views and streaks.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Think being verified on social media is cool? Now you can get verified on Wink by submitting a photo to prove your identity. Go get that check mark, and thanks for helping us keep our community safe! We’ve also made improvements like adding a countdown in random chat to decide whether you want to chat or not, plus other bug fixes and little things that make a big difference!

title: Wink - find & make new snapchat friends

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink: Unlimited friends! Wink is the best place to make new friends from all over the world. It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

So...what exactly do you do on the Wink app?

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through a bunch of new faces! Does that guy have the same quote in his bio as you do?! SWIPE RIGHT! Instant friends. She likes the soccer team that you hate the most?! SWIPE LEFT! No chance of a friendship there! On Wink, you can meet new friends in your country and around the world. You can add them on Snapchat, or start up a conversation right on Wink. You’ll see tons of new faces, read about them in their bios, and decide who you really want to be Wink friends or snap friends with! Start swiping to meet your new pals!

ADD
When you request to add someone or they request to add you, Wink makes it super easy to add the new friends you’re meeting to Wink and on Snapchat. With the click of a button, you become instantly connected! You go from a swipe on Wink, right to being friends!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new Wink friends is to start up the conversation right here on Wink! You have the option to add them on Snapchat as well, but why not chat a bit first? Get to know your new friends. Find out what you have in common! Who knows, someone you start messaging on Wink could become your lifelong best friend.

EARN
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on Wink! What are the gems used for, you ask? You can use gems to send add requests to your new friends, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing Wink with your existing snap friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. If you keep earning gems, unlimited friends is truly what there is on Wink.

Basically, what I’m trying to say is... you can never have too many friends. And tbh, it can be hard to make friends sometimes. All the awkwardness and asking for numbers and Snapchats and whatever. Wink exists to help you easily put yourself out there, and find more and more people to make your life even more fun! All you have to do is create your profile, tell everyone who you are, and start to discover your future besties.

But wait...there’s more! There are some other major bonuses to using Wink. Remember how I said you can not only chat with your new friends on the Wink app? Well you can also add them on Snapchat super easily! The more new friends you make and add to snap, the more views you get on your Snapchat story. You could go from 50 to 500 people watching! You’ll also have even more people to start snap streaks with (just make sure to keep those alive)!

Say yolo and just do it. Download the Wink app, put yourself out there, and see all of the cool people you can find by sitting there and mindlessly swiping while you watch TV even though you’re supposed to be doing homework. What do you have to lose? Go meet people to become friends with!!

PS - Wink is for friendships ONLY. Thank you.

Safety disclaimer: Wink is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with on both Wink and Snapchat Snapchat. Additionally, Wink is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Account selling, or requesting adult content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. title: Wink - find & make new snapchat friends

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink: Unlimited friends! Wink is the best place to make new friends from all over the world. It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

So...what exactly do you do on the Wink app?

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through a bunch of new faces! Does that girl love soccer too? SWIPE RIGHT! Instant friends. She likes the kind of music that you hate the most? SWIPE LEFT! No chance of a friendship there. On Wink, you can meet new friends in your country and around the world. You can start up the conversation right on Wink, and add them on Snapchat too. You’ll see tons of new faces, read about them in their bios, check out their interests, and decide who you really want to be Wink friends or snap friends with! Start swiping to meet your new pals!

ADD
When you request to add someone or they request to add you, Wink makes it super easy to add the new friends you’re meeting to Wink and on Snapchat. With the click of a button, you become instantly connected! You go from a swipe on Wink, right to being friends!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new Wink friends is to start up the conversation right here on Wink! You have the option to add them on Snapchat as well, but why not chat a bit first? Get to know your new friends. Find out what you have in common! You can also use the messenger on Wink to send messages, audio messages, photos, ice breakers, GIFs, and even play games against each other. If you’re looking for someone to talk to ASAP, try out Random Chat! You’ll be instantly connected to someone new, and you’ll have the option to add them as a friend from within the chat if you want to keep talking later! Who knows, someone you start messaging on Wink could become your lifelong best friend!

EARN
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on Wink! What are the gems used for, you ask? You can use gems to send add requests to your new friends, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. You can also use them in the WinkShop to buy a new background for your profile, or plant a tree in real life. Using your gems to make the world a better place? You’re the best! Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing Wink with your existing snap friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. Another way to get gems is to play super fun games in the Wink Arcade. The points you earn from the games will turn into gems! If you keep earning gems, unlimited friends is truly what you’ll find on Wink.

Basically, what I’m trying to say is... you can never have too many friends. And tbh, it can be hard to make friends sometimes. All the awkwardness and asking for numbers and Snapchats and whatever. Wink exists to help you easily put yourself out there, and find more and more people to make your life even more fun! All you have to do is create your profile, tell everyone who you are, and start to discover your future besties.

PS - Wink is for friendships ONLY. Thank you.

Safety disclaimer: Wink is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with. Although this communication with new friends doesn’t always happen on our platform, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing their location, full name, and all other personal information with new friends. Additionally, Wink is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Accounts selling, or requesting inappropriate content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. Please report anything you see that isn’t right!

Have feedback on Wink? Lmk what you like, don’t like, want to add, etc by emailing support@getwinkapp.com.

No chance of a friendship there. On Wink, you can meet new friends in your country and around the world. You can start up the conversation right on Wink, and add them on Snapchat too. You’ll see tons of new faces, read about them in their bios, check out their interests, and decide who you really want to be Wink friends or snap friends with! Start swiping to meet your new pals!

ADD
When you request to add someone or they request to add you, Wink makes it super easy to add the new friends you’re meeting to Wink and on Snapchat. With the click of a button, you become instantly connected! You go from a swipe on Wink, right to being friends!

CHAT

Get to know your new friends. Find out what you have in common! You can also use the messenger on Wink to send messages, audio messages, photos, ice breakers, GIFs, and even play games against each other. You’ll be instantly connected to someone new, and you’ll have the option to add them as a friend from within the chat if you want to keep talking later! Who knows, someone you start messaging on Wink could become your lifelong best friend!

EARN

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Wink has upgraded to BFF! We know change can be scary, but we promise this is the best kind of change! With Wink becoming BFF, we’ve been improving everything from bugs, to making it easier to find friends, to our safety and community guidelines. But don’t worry, it’s still the same app you loved before with your same friends, just with a new name. Update now and explore all the new friends and fun BFF has to offer! And thanks for being our besties!

title: BFF - make new friends / Wink

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
BFF is the best place to make new friends from all over the world! It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through tons of new faces from your own country or worldwide. Check out each person’s profile to decide if you think they could be your new BFF! That girl loves soccer, just like you? Swipe right! Instant BFFs. This guy likes the kind of music you can’t stand? Swipe left! No problem. On BFF, you can connect with so many people you have things in common with. Start swiping to meet your new besties!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new BFF is to send a message right here on the app! Within the BFF messenger, you can send messages, photos, ice breakers, GIFs, and audio messages. If you have a verified profile, you could even try an audio or video call. You’ll also have the option to add your new friends on Snapchat.

EXPRESS YOURSELF
Use your BFF profile to express yourself and make a great first impression! You can add up to 6 photos of yourself, add a bio that explains more about who you are, add your unique interests, record a voice intro, and change your profile colors using the BFFShop. Using interests is a great way to find friends who already have hobbies and passions in common with you! Not sure what you should or shouldn’t upload to your profile? Check out our photo guidelines at https://getbff.com/community!

EARN GEMS
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on BFF! You can use gems to send a friend request to someone new, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. You can also use gems to purchase a new background for your profile! Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing BFF with your existing friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. Keep earning gems to keep making new friends!

STAY SAFE
BFF is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with. Our team at BFF is very passionate about making this the best and safest app to make you feel more connected. Although this communication with new friends doesn’t always happen on our platform, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing location, full name, and all other personal information with new friends. Additionally, BFF is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Accounts selling, or requesting inappropriate content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. Please report anything you see that isn’t right! For more information on safety, visit https://getbff.com/safety. To read up on our Community Guidelines, visit https://getbff.com/community. Let’s work together to keep everyone safe on BFF!

Go be the friendly face someone needs to see and start meeting new friends on BFF!

Make sure to follow us on Instagram and TikTok at @getbff to keep up with the latest news and be part of the BFF community! Questions or concerns? Feel free to email our team at support@getbff.com.

PS - BFF is for friendships ONLY.

---

BFF is free to download and use. Additionally, users can choose to subscribe to BFF+ or purchase different gem or boost packs. Try BFF+ today for unlimited swiping, a free boost, and more awesome perks!

title: Wink - make new friends

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink is the best place to make new friends from all over the world! It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through tons of new faces from your own country or worldwide. Check out each person’s profile to decide if you think they could be your new friend! That girl loves soccer, just like you? Swipe right! Instant friends. This guy likes the kind of music you can’t stand? Swipe left! No problem. On Wink, you can connect with so many people you have things in common with. Start swiping to meet your new besties!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new friends is to send a message right here on the app! Within the Wink messenger, you can send messages, photos, ice breakers, GIFs, and audio messages. If you have a verified profile, you could even try an audio or video call. You’ll also have the option to add your new friends on Snapchat.

EXPRESS YOURSELF
Use your Wink profile to express yourself and make a great first impression! You can add up to 6 photos of yourself, add a bio that explains more about who you are, add your unique interests, record a voice intro, and change your profile colors using the Wink Shop. Using interests is a great way to find friends who already have hobbies and passions in common with you! Not sure what you should or shouldn’t upload to your profile? Check out our photo guidelines at https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/!

EARN GEMS
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on Wink! You can use gems to send a friend request to someone new, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. You can also use gems to purchase a new background for your profile! Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing Wink with your existing friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. Keep earning gems to keep making new friends!

STAY SAFE
Wink is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with. Our team at Wink is very passionate about making this the best and safest app to make you feel more connected. Although this communication with new friends doesn’t always happen on our platform, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing location, full name, and all other personal information with new friends. Additionally, Wink is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Accounts selling, or requesting inappropriate content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. Please report anything you see that isn’t right! For more information on safety, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/safety/. To read up on our Community Guidelines, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/. Let’s work together to keep everyone safe on Wink!

Go be the friendly face someone needs to see and start meeting new friends on Wink!

Questions or concerns? Feel free to email our team at support@getwinkapp.com.

PS - Wink is for friendships ONLY.

title: Wink - make new friends

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink is the best place to make new friends from all over the world! It’s as easy as swiping right and starting up a conversation with your potential new bestie.

SWIPE
Swipe right and left through tons of new faces from your own country or worldwide. Check out each person’s profile to decide if you think they could be your new friend! That girl loves soccer, just like you? Swipe right! Instant friends. This guy likes the kind of music you can’t stand? Swipe left! No problem. On Wink, you can connect with so many people you have things in common with. Start swiping to meet your new besties!

CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new friends is to send a message right here on the app! Within the Wink messenger, you can send messages, photos, ice breakers, GIFs, and audio messages. If you have a verified profile, you could even try an audio or video call.

EXPRESS YOURSELF
Use your Wink profile to express yourself and make a great first impression! You can add up to 6 photos of yourself, add a bio that explains more about who you are, add your unique interests, record a voice intro, and change your profile colors using the Wink Shop. Using interests is a great way to find friends who already have hobbies and passions in common with you! Not sure what you should or shouldn’t upload to your profile? Check out our photo guidelines at https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/!

EARN GEMS
You have the opportunity to earn gems every day on Wink! You can use gems to send a friend request to someone new, or to click the back arrow when you may have missed someone. You can also use gems to purchase a new background for your profile! Whether it’s a daily check-in or sharing Wink with your existing friends, there are tons of ways to get more gems. Keep earning gems to keep making new friends!

STAY SAFE
Wink is intended to be used for making new friends from all over the world to add and chat with. Our team at Wink is very passionate about making this the best and safest app to make you feel more connected. Although this communication with new friends doesn’t always happen on our platform, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing location, full name, and all other personal information with new friends. Additionally, Wink is not intended for the buying and selling of adult content. Accounts selling, or requesting inappropriate content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. Please report anything you see that isn’t right! For more information on safety, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/safety/. To read up on our Community Guidelines, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/. Let’s work together to keep everyone safe on Wink!

Go be the friendly face someone needs to see and start meeting new friends on Wink!

Questions or concerns? Feel free to email our team at support@getwinkapp.com.

PS - Wink is for friendships ONLY.

creator: 9 Count
descriptionHtml:
Wink is the best place to make new friends and more wherever you are! It’s as easy as looking through nearby profiles and starting up a conversation.

EXPLORE NEARBY
It’s now easier than ever to make friends IRL with Wink. Swipe through profiles of people near you, and find friends with common interests! Looking for a concert buddy? Connect with someone who likes the same genres of music! In a new city and looking to check out some coffee shops? Match with a fellow coffee lover nearby. Whatever types of connections you’re looking for, Wink’s got you covered!

EXPRESS YOURSELF
Create your Wink profile, and put out the vibes you’re hoping to get back! You can add up to 6 photos of yourself, add your unique interests, write a descriptive bio, record a voice intro, and change your profile colors. Using interests is a great way to find friends who already have hobbies and passions in common with you. Not sure what you should or shouldn’t upload to your profile? Check out our photo guidelines at https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/!


CHAT
The fastest and safest way to chat with your new connections is to send a message! Within the Wink messenger, you can send messages, photos, and audio messages. Make sure to exercise caution when talking with someone new, on Wink and the internet in general!


STAY SAFE
Wink is a fun and safe community to make friends nearby and around the world. Our team is passionate about maintaining the highest standards of safety for all of our users. If you see any behaviors that put the safety of the community at risk, please report them using the in-app report function, and support@getwink.app.com if you would like to provide more details. Additionally, we urge our users to be mindful when considering sharing specific details like location, full name, and all other personal information with new connections. Buying and selling of adult content on Wink is prohibited. Accounts selling, or requesting inappropriate content will be disabled due to violating our community guidelines. For more information on safety, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/safety/. To read up on our Community Guidelines, visit https://www.getwinkapp.com/community/. Let’s work together to keep everyone safe on Wink!

Wink is intended for making friends, but you never know where a connection could go ;)
